Title: Implement File Ingestion Framework with Apache Iceberg Reader Support

Description:
Develop a file ingestion framework to support Apache Iceberg table format reading capabilities, enabling efficient data processing and analytics workflows.

Acceptance Criteria:

1. Framework Configuration
- Implement configuration parser for Iceberg reader settings
- Support basic authentication mechanisms
- Enable custom table location specification

2. Iceberg Reader Implementation
- Create reader component for Iceberg table format
- Handle schema evolution and partitioning
- Support snapshot isolation and time travel queries

3. Data Processing
- Implement streaming and batch read operations
- Enable column pruning and predicate pushdown
- Handle nested data structures

4. Error Handling
- Implement comprehensive error handling for read failures
- Provide detailed logging and monitoring capabilities
- Add retry mechanisms for transient failures

5. Testing & Documentation
- Write unit tests with >80% coverage
- Create integration test suite
- Document API specifications and usage examples
